div.p: new_block = block + HEADER + size new_block->size = block->size - size - HEADER new_block->free = 1 new_block->magic = HEAP_MAGIC new_block->next = block->next new_block->prev = block block->size = size

ul.li: Time: O(n) worst case, n = number of blocks
Space: O(1) additional memory Key Invariants:
No two adjacent free blocks (after coalesce)
